  h-c1:
    type: CONDITION
    statement: The clusterability mechanism operates effectively in mid-capacity models
      (ResNet-50 with 88.5% baseline WGA, 11.5% headroom) on datasets with discrete
      minority groups (Waterbirds 4-group structure), but hits ceiling effects in
      high-capacity models (ViT-H-14 at 90%+ baseline, <10% headroom) and fails on
      datasets without clear spurious group structure where clustering assumptions
      break down
    status: NOT_STARTED
